1 EVIDENCE SUPPORTING THE FACTOR IS NOT PRESENTED TO THE COURT, THE
2 COURT SHALL MAKE NOTE OF THE FACTORS NOT CONSIDERED IN ITS DECISION.
3 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
4 October 1, 2025.

